---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageHero from '../../components/PageHero.astro';
---
<Layout title="RC Cares" description="RC Cares is Rest Church's community outreach ministry, serving San Antonio with the practical love of Christ.">
  <PageHero eyebrow="Community Outreach" title="RC Cares" subtitle="Serving San Antonio with the practical love of Christ — meeting needs, building bridges, and sharing the hope of the Gospel." breadcrumb={[{ label:'Ministries', href:'/ministries' }, { label:'RC Cares', href:'' }]} bgImage="https://brazengrace.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/gc5.jpg" />

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="ministry-layout">
        <div class="ministry-main">
          <h2>About RC Cares</h2>
          <p>RC Cares is the community outreach arm of Rest Church, dedicated to serving the people of San Antonio with the love of Jesus Christ in practical, tangible ways. We believe the Gospel is not just a message to be preached — it's a life to be lived, and that includes caring for our neighbors.</p>
          <p>We are committed to being the hands and feet of Jesus in our city, meeting people where they are and demonstrating that God cares for every dimension of human life — physical, emotional, and spiritual.</p>

          <h3>What We Do</h3>
          <div class="what-grid">
            {[
              { title:'Community Service',  desc:'Organized service projects that meet practical needs in the San Antonio community.' },
              { title:'Prayer Ministry',    desc:'Bringing hope and prayer to those who are hurting, lonely, or in need.' },
              { title:'Resource Support',   desc:'Connecting people with resources, support, and assistance in times of need.' },
              { title:'Gospel Outreach',    desc:'Sharing the message of grace and the love of God with those who have yet to hear.' },
            ].map(w => (
              <div class="what-card">
                <h4>{w.title}</h4>
                <p>{w.desc}</p>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>

          <h3>Get Involved</h3>
          <p>RC Cares thrives because of people who are passionate about making a difference in their city. Whether you want to volunteer for a single event or become a regular part of the outreach team, there's a place for you.</p>
          <p>For more information about upcoming outreach opportunities, contact us directly.</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Volunteer With RC Cares</a>
        </div>

        <aside class="ministry-sidebar">
          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h4>Outreach Info</h4>
            <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">Focus</span><span>Community Outreach</span></div>
            <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">Location</span><span>San Antonio, TX</span></div>
            <div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">How</span><span>Volunteer &amp; Serve</span></div>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary" style="width:100%; justify-content:center; margin-top:1.25rem;">Get Involved</a>
          </div>
          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h4>Other Ministries</h4>
            <ul class="sidebar-links">
              <li><a href="/ministries/epic-life-groups">EPIC Life Groups →</a></li>
              <li><a href="/ministries/rc-youth">RC Youth →</a></li>
              <li><a href="/ministries/rc-kidz">RC Kidz →</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .ministry-layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 300px; gap: 3.5rem; align-items: start; }
  .ministry-main h2 { font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .ministry-main h3 { font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--navy); margin: 2rem 0 .85rem; }
  .ministry-main p  { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.85; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .what-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; margin: 1rem 0 1.5rem; }
  .what-card { padding: 1.25rem; background: var(--cream); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); }
  .what-card h4 { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: .4rem; }
  .what-card p  { font-size: .84rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; }
  .sidebar-card { background: var(--cream); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
  .sidebar-card h4 { font-size: .7rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 1rem; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }
  .info-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; gap: .5rem; font-size: .875rem; padding: .55rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .info-row:last-of-type { border-bottom: none; }
  .info-label { font-weight: 600; color: var(--navy); }
  .sidebar-links { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .5rem; }
  .sidebar-links a { font-size: .875rem; color: var(--navy); font-weight: 500; transition: color var(--transition); }
  .sidebar-links a:hover { color: var(--gold); }
  @media (max-width: 860px) { .ministry-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .what-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
</style>
